{"word":"G3895 - παραπίπτω - parapíptō - par-ap-ip'-to - Fall away","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραπίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parapíptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ap-ip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fall away</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மறுதலித்துப்போ"},{"paragraph":"to fall beside a person or thing; to slip aside; to deviate from the right path, turn aside, wander"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>; to <i>fall aside</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>apostatize:</i> - fall away.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1601/1601\">G1601</a>, <a href=\"#/G2667/2667\">G2667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3895/3895\">G3895</a>, <a href=\"#/G3900/3900\">G3900</a>, <a href=\"#/G4045/4045\">G4045</a>, <a href=\"#/G4098/4098\">G4098</a>, <a href=\"#/G4430/4430\">G4430</a>, <a href=\"#/G4431/4431\">G4431</a>"}]}